node.text: What a great day. Unbelievable vibes. I love that little turkey more than anything in the whole world. She put so much time & effort into the planning of our big day. Happy & blessed. I’ll have the whole video soon, not really sure about posting it yet, but I’ll keep y’all updated. P&L

node.text:
I’m blessed.

Blessed to have my father around.
Blessed for our relationship.
Blessed to have his guidance.

And I think it’s important to take a minute, hit the brakes, and really be thankful, especially on days like this. 

Happy Fathers Day 💪🏼❤️

node.text:
#MFAMGBT - We’re gettin’ better out here everyday. Mind, body, overall health. 

It’s been fun sharing the workouts with ya’ll & seeing so many of you jump in & get involved with the initiative. Remember that anybody can get after it, all ya need really is 2 things, dedication & consistency. 

Most of you know & understand this, but for the few that don’t, the first 2 weeks suck, because ya gotta “pay the man”. The rest is fuckin’ easy baby, as it becomes a part of who you are. 

Good luck out there, ThorCock believes in you 💪🏼
